<HEADLINE> Organization of Eastern Caribbean States Gets UNDP Support </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, February 3 (Xinhua) -- The United Nations
Development Program (UNDP) is helping the Organization of Eastern
Caribbean States (OECS) modernize its information management and
communications system and create a human and social development
unit.
</P>
<P>
