Tuesday at Rongai divisional headquarters of Nakuru district
between Kalenjin and Kikuyu elders.
</P>
<P>
The meeting decided that more police posts be created in the
troubled areas of the Rift Valley province.
</P>
<P>
The elders held that the violence which killed about 100
people in the past several weeks was "political" and had nothing
to do with ethnicity. 
