Five linesmen have also been selected from Asia. They are
Mohamed Ahmed Al Musawi of Oman, Hussein Ghadanfari of Kuwait,
Halim Halim Abdul Hamid of Malaysia, YounHyun Jeon of South Korea
and Muhamad Wickeramatunge Samarathna of Sri Lanka.
</P>
<P>
FIFA said the officials, altogether 34 referees and 33
linesman, would still have to pass a fitness test. 
